subject: Golf
lead_paragraph: Garrett Willis shot a 10-under 62 on the TPC Summerlin course for a share of the second-round lead in the Frys.com Open in Las Vegas. D. J. Trahan and the rookie George McNeill matched Willis at 13-under 130. McNeill shot a seven-under 64 on the par-71 TPC The Canyons course and Trahan had a 64 on the same course in an event missing all of the world’s top-20 players.
